text: A landlocked parcel is a real estate plot that has no legal access to a public right of way.What Does Landlocked Mean?, SFGate A landlocked parcel has less value than a parcel that is not landlocked.What Is Landlocked Property Worth?, Sapling Often, the owner of a landlocked parcel can obtain access to a public roadway by easement.Who Would Ever Want A Landlocked Property?, landcentral == See also == * Landlocked country == References == Category:Real estate
title: Landlocked parcel
